query:
SELECT 
  countryCode,
  serviceType,
  serviceLevel,
  rateUsdCents,
  isServiceable,
  CASE 
    WHEN isServiceable = 1 THEN 'Available'
    WHEN isServiceable = 0 THEN 'Excluded'
    ELSE 'NULL'
  END as status
FROM supplierRates 
WHERE supplierId = 240001 
  AND countryCode = 'AU'
ORDER BY serviceType, serviceLevel;
